      "writtenOn": "2019-08-19T21:30:36Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "As previously discussed, I’m not a big fan of this. I’d feel somewhat differently if Initialize() were reachable any way other than a direct call to Write(). But since it’s essentially just hoisting a bit of conditionalized code out of Write(), I think it just makes things harder to follow.",
