      "writtenOn": "2019-08-19T21:30:36Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I can’t imagine why you would even need this. This is the kind of thing that it’s OK to write in-line in the test. But if you absolutely insist, this doesn’t make use of any object context at all, so it shouldn’t be const, it should be static.",
      "revId": "fe231a5ef7e78ab56dcf18bb10a32d6b8f2e3a61",
