      },
      "lineNbr": 46,
      "author": {
        "id": 1000825
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-08-19T23:58:17Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "In the test, I test the compressed data is less or larger than the buffer. It return the length of the buffer, and can\u0027t be static, right?",
      "parentUuid": "1b539d75_2f92e54f",
      "revId": "fe231a5ef7e78ab56dcf18bb10a32d6b8f2e3a61",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
